page.title: 03HULLBRIDGE
page.content: Hullbridge is a place with lots of houses and lots of shops.It is very hilly and lots of people live there.There is hardly any grass or field land.When we went to Hullbridge we made a long list of shops down Ferry Road.Also we made a list of how many banks and other shops there were.It was very tiring walking down Ferry Road because it is so long but we enjoyed looking at the shops and seeing the different names.Some of the names were quite stange like Seperate Ways,Budgen,The Ferry Pharmacy,Ivory Cosmetics,Claydons,The Ferry Fishers and the Sweat Oak.Down Ferry Road there are 22 shops.
